MIME media type name : Application

MIME subtype name : Vendor Tree - vnd.epson.ssf

Required parameters : none

Optional parameters : 
none

Encoding considerations : 
As the content is in binary,a suitable encoding should be used.

Security considerations : 
Seiko Epson Corp. refuses to give out information that can be used to
evaluate the security implications of the MIME type.As such,the
security implications of using this type cannot be assessed and there
may be substantial risks is using this type.

Interoperability considerations : 


Published specification : 
It is not an opened specification and no published document is
available. Seiko Epson Corp. controls the specification.

Applications which use this media : 
following applications of Seiko Epson Corp. and any licensed company,
QUASS Stream Player Plugin
QUASS Stream Player for Embedded System
